                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d558">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Combs</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Guatemala</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1903-03-23">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 23, 1903</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Combs reports that the Government of Guatemala, in maintaining its
                    constitution, refuses to recognize the American citizenship of Alberto, Posadas,
                    a native-born Guatemalan returning bearing a United States passport, and that
                    the naturalized citizen referred to is under detention for refusal to pay a
                    forced loan.</p>
                <p>Mr. Combs requests instructions.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
